Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode title: Special?

Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.39,0:01:03.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:11.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya is the one I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.15,0:01:20.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.50,0:01:29.02,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.82,0:01:33.03,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they going to be dating?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.39,0:01:38.76,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there going to be someone special for Kazehaya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.40,0:01:43.29,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to help make that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:45.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Sawako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:47.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.13,0:01:49.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:52.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.53,0:02:04.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.50,0:02:07.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:12.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.46,0:02:31.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I wouldn't be a good match with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.64,0:02:34.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.48,0:02:38.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I want you to cheer me on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.73,0:02:43.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only person I've told.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.74,0:02:48.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe he should be with someone else after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:53.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:58.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I think you'd be a good couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:00.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako-chan, then—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.52,0:03:01.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:08.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't cheer for you honestly, so I can't help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.84,0:03:13.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Kazehaya-kun is special to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:18.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I can't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.91,0:03:25.94,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything else I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.94,0:03:31.69,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun must be special to her, just like he is to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:39.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help, but I know how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.45,0:03:41.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can at least listen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:43.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:49.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you back off?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.57,0:03:55.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the part where you're supposed to know your place and back off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:59.59,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear it from Kurumi-chan's direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:03.09,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Is someone behind her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:04.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.83,0:04:07.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean you know how I feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:10.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to go out with Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:13.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, never.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:15.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean special?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:16.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:18.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he was nice to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.74,0:04:21.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he talked to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:23.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he was kind to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:25.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:27.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just volunteer work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:32.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't even have to be Kazehaya, as long as they're nice to you, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.03,0:04:36.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kurumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:40.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fair, Sawako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:45.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because you're gloomy and you scare everyone off,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:49.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya talks to you and you don't even make an effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:56.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to work hard when you're cute and popular like I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:03.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kurumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.69,0:05:10.98,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew it was so tough being popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:18.21,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,And that I was having it easy being gloomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:25.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fair, just because you're a bit cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:27.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:31.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so stuck up just because you're cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:33.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K.O.!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:36.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:39.06,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like what Kurumi-chan said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:45.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fair, Sawako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:48.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya talks to you and you don't even make an effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:51.89,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.89,0:05:56.62,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just lending myself to his kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.68,0:06:02.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't even have to be Kazehaya, as long as they're nice to you, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:06.81,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.81,0:06:12.09,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,What if someone other than Kazehaya-kun was nice to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.75,0:06:18.80,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'd have felt the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.30,0:06:22.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.39,0:06:25.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:28.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sports day!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:30.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do or die, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:32.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:39.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think? Do I stand out in my red t-shirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.22,0:06:40.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:41.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:43.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It brings out the idiot in you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:44.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:45.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're flattering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:49.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshida-san looks awesome in red.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.19,0:06:52.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu looks so blissful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.11,0:06:57.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, the girls' soccer match is right before our game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:07:00.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go cheer them on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.76,0:07:01.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.89,0:07:05.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't be a bunch of jackasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:06.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just going to cheer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:08.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:10.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:13.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:19.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:21.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.55,0:07:22.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:24.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:25.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:28.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:29.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:30.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:31.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:48.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:07:56.08,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.23,0:07:58.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the zashiki-warashi effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:02.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me try.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:06.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.43,0:08:07.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:08.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:10.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:12.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:14.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're treating you like a goddess of fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:16.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've sure made some ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:19.72,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'm part of the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:21.35,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Kazehaya-kun effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:35.53,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I feel this way because he helps me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:39.08,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it nothing special?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:41.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:42.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:42.80,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Forwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.80,0:08:43.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:44.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:47.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3-2 with stoppage time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:51.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think our girls will outrun them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.16,0:08:52.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet we will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.27,0:08:54.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our red devil's pulling a hat trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:02.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my god, Chizu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.84,0:09:04.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How flashy do you need to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:07.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, where's Sadako?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:09.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:10.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's there, right, Ryu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.89,0:09:11.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.56,0:09:13.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.68,0:09:15.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's she now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.72,0:09:17.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she teleporting?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.38,0:09:21.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's sort of fitting in now, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:22.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.28,0:09:28.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's been less gloomy since she's become friends with Yano and Yoshida.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.74,0:09:37.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh shit, there's no one there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:40.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sa—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.01,0:09:49.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:52.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.52,0:09:59.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She kicked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.59,0:10:01.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:05.21,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I kicked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:10.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? My shoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.08,0:10:16.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.46,0:10:18.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:23.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.12,0:10:38.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.73,0:10:40.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fourth goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:45.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Game over!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.60,0:10:48.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.55,0:10:50.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Sadako!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:53.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:56.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:10:58.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:04.92,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:08.86,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've celebrated with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.86,0:11:10.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.35,0:11:22.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all that practice you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:24.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Viva practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.85,0:11:41.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.54,0:11:44.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to go strategize before the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:46.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.34,0:11:48.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a game next?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:50.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, softball.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:53.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.62,0:11:54.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.54,0:11:56.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hit 'em hard. Hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:58.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your elbow hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:12:01.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Godspeed! Godspeed! Godspeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:12:01.24,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Ow. Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:04.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.59,0:12:07.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll win.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:11.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you, Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:14.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about me, Yano-chin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:17.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was huge in that game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:18.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really showy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.81,0:12:19.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And red.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.58,0:12:21.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:25.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we have to go practice volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.73,0:12:29.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, before the big game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:31.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have over an hour before the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:34.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What to do, Sadako?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.68,0:12:37.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go find my shoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.26,0:12:39.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you lose it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:42.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sort of got carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.97,0:12:45.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, go pick up your shoe and come watch our—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:48.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she's going to go cheer at the softball match.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:52.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't go watch the boys' softball game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.09,0:12:56.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go cheer for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.16,0:12:58.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.43,0:13:01.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.06,0:13:02.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go watch volleyball too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:05.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.77,0:13:07.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:10.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.77,0:13:12.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.61,0:13:18.31,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheerleading?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:21.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lose what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:23.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We already won in soccer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:26.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:40.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.07,0:13:46.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi-chan, did you pick that up for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:49.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.86,0:13:55.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, she picked up her shoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:13:57.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.93,0:14:00.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Sawako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.31,0:14:03.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:06.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.10,0:14:07.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:09.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.46,0:14:10.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.65,0:14:15.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I went too far yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.85,0:14:16.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.80,0:14:19.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.99,0:14:25.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me Kurumi-chan anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.31,0:14:29.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:30.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ume-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:42.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're on my people-who-called-me-Ume list.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.14,0:14:47.07,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in her diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:50.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.19,0:14:52.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of response is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:55.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.28,0:14:57.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Ume-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:14:59.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.20,0:15:02.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What do I call you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:10.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“Ume” is my one hang-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:12.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.13,0:15:13.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.57,0:15:16.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My grandma gave me this shabby old name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.42,0:15:18.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't suit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.49,0:15:22.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shabby? Old? But it's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:23.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.89,0:15:26.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.56,0:15:27.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Sawako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:33.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your name's just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:39.91,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, she always called me Sawako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:44.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you want to go to the field with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:47.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.49,0:15:49.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's going to be a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:50.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun's playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:52.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.23,0:16:01.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.46,0:16:09.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's seems a little different to me now, but she's still cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:13.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to watch the game with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:15.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you whispering?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:15.11,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi-chan's watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.11,0:16:15.90,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Try calling her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.90,0:16:19.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, I have my own problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.49,0:16:21.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kurumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.47,0:16:27.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help but speak my mind when I talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:35.09,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She tells me what she's really thinking now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:36.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:37.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:03.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's waving at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:05.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.09,0:17:07.78,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:09.31,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,That was to Kurumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.31,0:17:10.84,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:13.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's so many girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:15.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was that girl next to Sadako?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:17.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:19.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:21.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of Sadako,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.03,0:17:23.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That soccer game...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:25.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.03,0:17:27.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.55,0:17:28.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:29.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flash of light!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:31.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's awesome now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.29,0:17:32.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:34.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.98,0:17:37.42,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they praising her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.42,0:17:39.05,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:43.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Sadako's not her name, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.44,0:17:45.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it? Kuronuma Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:50.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Chizuru told me her real name before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,0:17:52.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:54.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:55.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of “Takako.”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:17:59.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was an easy way to remember, an image.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:02.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark water in a swamp...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:05.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It starts with “Sa.”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:07.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakako.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.09,0:18:07.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:12.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It starts with “Sa,” and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.76,0:18:15.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something like Tawashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.23,0:18:16.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sa—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.02,0:18:17.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.19,0:18:18.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:23.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuranuma Sawako.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:25.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.01,0:18:26.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it Doronuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:28.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.55,0:18:31.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let's play catch before the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.35,0:18:32.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:35.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:38.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouta, you're with me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.23,0:18:39.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:43.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:54.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I looked up the word “special” in the dictionary yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:56.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dictionary?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.39,0:18:59.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“Unable to be treated like everything or everyone else.”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:01.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.72,0:19:05.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dictionaries are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:07.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like they're listening to us talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.38,0:19:09.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your point?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.07,0:19:13.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, just that it's tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.97,0:19:20.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to think of Kazehaya-kun as being that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:25.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that he's always been helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.42,0:19:30.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that he's been helping me for as long as I've known him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.24,0:19:36.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't compare him to everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.29,0:19:42.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's only because you don't talk to the other boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.72,0:19:46.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try talking to them more?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:49.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, like someone that sits close to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:51.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.39,0:19:52.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:54.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.28,0:19:55.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind you or in front or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:57.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.01,0:19:58.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.58,0:20:00.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:03.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've talked to Sanada-kun a bit before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.01,0:20:05.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanada?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.91,0:20:10.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this, Joe's magical special pitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:12.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:30.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu! Nice cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.94,0:20:32.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No magic pitches.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:33.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:37.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:39.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.52,0:20:40.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry. I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:40.88,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,See,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.61,0:20:43.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you got helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:48.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to thank him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.69,0:20:50.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot, I was too stunned.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.67,0:20:52.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:54.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should go thank him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.59,0:20:57.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you should talk to him more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:02.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.93,0:22:30.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Following him with my eyes, following him with my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.30,0:22:34.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Romance
